{"tid":411852,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇絲打甩好多頭髪","createTime":"2017-09-24T07:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T10:27:45.000Z","uid":147685,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ade1479a5b9353c7e3585aab4928d95728a03014","tid":411852,"uid":147685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:20:46.000Z","msg":"每朝一梳頭就成地頭髮 <br />\n洗完頭又甩好多 <br />\n淨係染過兩次頭 仲要係深啡冇漂過<br />\n之前間中都會用下捲髮棒 而家完全唔敢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經成日用護髮素但都係冇用<br />\n仲有頭皮(但唔係污糟嗰隻 因為我係好怕頭笠嘅人)<br />\n真係完全唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前啲頭髮又厚又長<br />\n而家又薄又長得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171663d29ae0f8a329e015ba91a368e041a57bad","tid":411852,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"每人每日都會甩百零條頭髮 正常架喎<br />\n護髮素係令你頭髮順滑咋喎<br />\n同埋你唔好搽咁近頭皮<br />\n我無用護髮素好耐<br />\n自己食返多啲對頭髮好既野仲好啦"},{"pid":"5990cee0877d0aecd425f15b5b727a600359a66d","tid":411852,"uid":147685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:32:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每人每日都會甩百零條頭髮 正常架喎<br />\n護髮素係令你頭髮順滑咋喎<br />\n同埋你唔好搽咁近頭皮<br />\n我無用護髮素好耐<br />\n自己食返多啲對頭髮好既野仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n我知呀但我係髮線越甩越疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用護髮素係因為以為頭髮傷先甩咁多<br />\n有冇食啲咩嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac44221cd8b8d0903b3913eed28905ce60debcf8","tid":411852,"uid":130339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:37:44.000Z","msg":"甩爆多頭髮<br />\n頭髮好厚 但係甩完都係好厚<br />\n隻手每wea一次頭髮就甩幾條<br />\n成日一吸塵就發現床邊全部都係頭髮<br />\n同埋生得勁慢 10個月只係由啱啱掂到胸到啱啱冚晒個胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb6d48907377060688ef23d8473205d5a5b5aae","tid":411852,"uid":60291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甩爆多頭髮<br />\n頭髮好厚 但係甩完都係好厚<br />\n隻手每wea一次頭髮就甩幾條<br />\n成日一吸塵就發現床邊全部都係頭髮<br />\n同埋生得勁慢 10個月只係由啱啱掂到胸到啱啱冚晒個胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eabbfe3b68207c1add9a5e1c63ab72384e079b6","tid":411852,"uid":92016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:43:03.000Z","msg":"一搽護髮素就係咁甩 搽極都仲有頭髮甩<br />\n平時都會無啦啦自己甩<br />\n撩到個大脾勁痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過家母話正常係新陳代謝既表現 就由得佢了"},{"pid":"396039a948ff6d7a093da620bf2da52a5e8db62f","tid":411852,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每人每日都會甩百零條頭髮 正常架喎<br />\n護髮素係令你頭髮順滑咋喎<br />\n同埋你唔好搽咁近頭皮<br />\n我無用護髮素好耐<br />\n自己食返多啲對頭髮好既野仲好啦</blockquote><br />\n我知呀但我係髮線越甩越疏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用護髮素係因為以為頭髮傷先甩咁多<br />\n有冇食啲咩嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都係咩黑豆黑芝麻核桃 好多。。"},{"pid":"5c7812457d370d1ff1d96398755e4a27278a73d7","tid":411852,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>甩爆多頭髮<br />\n頭髮好厚 但係甩完都係好厚<br />\n隻手每wea一次頭髮就甩幾條<br />\n成日一吸塵就發現床邊全部都係頭髮<br />\n同埋生得勁慢 10個月只係由啱啱掂到胸到啱啱冚晒個胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常每月長1-1.5cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甩係好正常 每日每人百零條係正常"},{"pid":"9bd943513638db4a87547561496fb189ea751cb1","tid":411852,"uid":138799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:56:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一搽護髮素就係咁甩 搽極都仲有頭髮甩<br />\n平時都會無啦啦自己甩<br />\n撩到個大脾勁痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過家母話正常係新陳代謝既表現 就由得佢了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n護髮素唔係for唔甩頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係令你頭髮順滑返無咁毛"},{"pid":"142995751e2c4822890904cd61e0b5bcd2ef3c20","tid":411852,"uid":130339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>甩爆多頭髮<br />\n頭髮好厚 但係甩完都係好厚<br />\n隻手每wea一次頭髮就甩幾條<br />\n成日一吸塵就發現床邊全部都係頭髮<br />\n同埋生得勁慢 10個月只係由啱啱掂到胸到啱啱冚晒個胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常每月長1-1.5cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甩係好正常 每日每人百零條係正常</blockquote><br />\n我10個月應該長咗8cm都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78544e6d14a1ee5f5fc78a78ee2fbb5ea39d054e","tid":411852,"uid":147685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一搽護髮素就係咁甩 搽極都仲有頭髮甩<br />\n平時都會無啦啦自己甩<br />\n撩到個大脾勁痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過家母話正常係新陳代謝既表現 就由得佢了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n護髮素唔係for唔甩頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係令你頭髮順滑返無咁毛</blockquote><br />\n我係毛燥加甩頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 集所有衰野於一身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83510ad7bfdf96927222878cfadff40a35241f61","tid":411852,"uid":147685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>甩爆多頭髮<br />\n頭髮好厚 但係甩完都係好厚<br />\n隻手每wea一次頭髮就甩幾條<br />\n成日一吸塵就發現床邊全部都係頭髮<br />\n同埋生得勁慢 10個月只係由啱啱掂到胸到啱啱冚晒個胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正常每月長1-1.5cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n甩係好正常 每日每人百零條係正常</blockquote><br />\n我10個月應該長咗8cm都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg